MacRuby: Cocoa so hot it will burn the roof of your mouth

This is the source for the presentation given at [Arlington Ruby Meetup](http://arlingtonruby.org) Nov 30th 2011.

The slides are in showoff format, and can be viewed by installing the `showff` gem and running the following:

    cd slides
    showoff serve

Once the server is running visit http://localhost:9090
